[It is not stated whether the serotype of _Salmonella enterica_ is reported in either cluster and whether they were identical by genetic testing. Either way, issues clearly occurred previous to the larger outbreak but it is not clear who knew and when it was known regarding the 1st cluster. - Mod.LL

